tspan.tspan: Server returns a "static" page with neccesary
scripts to update the page on the client
Client requests a partial "page", for example a list
This is cached, and the partial will only be fetched
Client makes an initial requst to the server
The partial is returned with code which by "magic"
can load the data required to render the page
The partial request the data neccesary to render
Data is returned, typically as JSON
